de.fhg.biomos.sensorplatform.deprecated

Class FarosEmotion360lib

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.fhg.biomos.sensorplatform.deprecated.FarosEmotion360lib

  • public abstract class FarosEmotion360lib
extends Object
    Three channel heart rate sensor. Instead of the standard Bluetooth specification, it uses BlueRadios serial port (BRSP) which is complicated to implement. General data (e.g. device name) is available through standard specification. In the resource folder there is an example program for android, how to use BRSP. Due to heavy reliance on the Android framework, this solution is not easily applicable to the Sensorplatform.
    Author:
    Daniel Pyka
